desc: A family run cafe located in North Bondi, The Depot is next to the iconic Bondi Beach. Sourcing local and sustainable produce. Serving all day breakfast, coffee and lunch. Enjoy freshly made pastries from our in-house bakery. We offer a spacious interior and plenty of outdoor seating.

layout.text: Sourcing local and sustainable produce, The Depot has an ever changing menu that highlights the seasons.
